<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 More than words that we can say
 More than air that we can breathe
 Is Your love forever calling
 love forever young
 love forever bleeding
 for me

[V2]
 More than things that we can do
 more than days than we can lose
 Is Your cross forever telling
 A place to keep in mind
 when You said that &quot;it is finished!&quot;
 for sure

[V3]
 Here I am back home again
 where's the reason of my life
 For this son of Yours
 was dead but now he's alive

[V4]
 I was lost but now I'm found
 So it's time to celebrate
 for this modern prodigal son</lyrics>
<title>Modern prodigal son</title>
<author>Marco Prezioso</author>
<hymn_number>1689</hymn_number>
</song>